<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Official Gecko Codes Thread]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=281&amp;p=2304#p2304"><![CDATA[
<span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: 116%;">Level Reset Codes</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Level Reset</span> (Y) [<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1v0aAtA5gG6Ax_G2yDqgnks5RNfylFkxT1r-NMPBbHTA/edit?pli=1" class="postlink">Harper/hellool</a>]<br />GameCube<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>01107040 00000000<br />0110701C 00000000<br />289F38B8 00000800<br />011A53C8 00000002<br />011A539E 00000008<br />031A53E2 00000000<br />031A5398 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br />Classic<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>01107040 00000000<br />0110701C 00000000<br />282085EA 00000020<br />011A53C8 00000002<br />011A539E 00000008<br />031A53E2 00000000<br />031A5398 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Star Select</span> (X) [<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1v0aAtA5gG6Ax_G2yDqgnks5RNfylFkxT1r-NMPBbHTA/edit?pli=1" class="postlink">Harper/hellool/abitalive</a>]<br />GameCube<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>289F38B8 00000400<br />291A53C8 0000000D<br />011A539E 00000008<br />031A53B8 00000004<br />011A53C8 00000001<br />031A53CA 0000020A<br />E0000000 80008000<br />289F38B8 00000400<br />2B1A53C8 0000000D<br />2B1A53C8 0000010D<br />2B1A53C8 00000000<br />011A539E 00000008<br />031A53B8 00000004<br />011A53C8 00000001<br />031A53CA 0000010A<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br />Classic<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>282085EA 00000008<br />291A53C8 0000000D<br />011A539E 00000008<br />031A53B8 00000004<br />011A53C8 00000001<br />031A53CA 0000020A<br />E0000000 80008000<br />282085EA 00000008<br />2B1A53C8 0000000D<br />2B1A53C8 0000010D<br />2B1A53C8 00000000<br />011A539E 00000008<br />031A53B8 00000004<br />011A53C8 00000001<br />031A53CA 0000010A<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: 116%;">Timer Codes</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">JS V1.1 Manual Timer</span> (X or Y) [<a href="https://sites.google.com/site/jamesskingdom/Home/game-codes-by-james-s/super-mario-64-codes#TOC-Timer-codes" class="postlink">James Stuart</a>]<br />GameCube<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>050B3808 A03BB25E<br />050B7DFC A1A000EE<br />010B5317 00000040<br />050B3810 00000000<br />289F38B8 00000400<br />031A53EC 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000<br />289F38B8 00000800<br />031A53EC 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br />Classic<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>050B3808 A03BB25E<br />050B7DFC A1A000EE<br />010B5317 00000040<br />050B3810 00000000<br />282085EA 00000008<br />031A53EC 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000<br />282085EA 00000020<br />031A53EC 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Remove TIME Text</span><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>031A2528 00000000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Automatically Reset Timer at Star Select</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=20&amp;t=279&amp;start=20#p2815" class="postlink">abitalive</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>291A53B8 00000004<br />031A53EC 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Make Timer Display Number Of Frames</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=319" class="postlink">Vegard</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>0514DBC4 10000031<br />0114DBC3 0000002A</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Precise Timer</span> [<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r4qGIL81YHg" target="_blank" class="postlink">GameZeldaYugioh</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>0314DB48 00002401<br />0314DB4A 0000000A<br />0314DB80 00000321<br />0314DB82 00000018<br />0314DB84 00000000<br />0314DB86 00004812<br />0314DB88 00002401<br />0314DB8A 00000003<br />0314DB8C 00000121<br />0314DB8E 0000001A<br />0314DB90 00000000<br />0314DB92 00005012<br />0314DB94 0000A7AA<br />0314DB96 00000024<br />0114DBE3 000000B4</code></dd></dl><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: 116%;">Other Codes</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Savestates on VC 2.1</span> (D-pad Down to save, D-pad Up to load) [<a href="https://sites.google.com/site/sm64gameshark/codes/savestates-on-n64" class="postlink">Kaze</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>03135340 000027BD<br />03135342 0000FFF0<br />03135344 0000AFBF<br />03135346 0000000C<br />03135348 00003C08<br />0313534A 00008033<br />0313534C 00003C09<br />0313534E 00008036<br />03135350 00003C0A<br />03135352 0000803F<br />03135354 00003C18<br />03135356 00008034<br />03135358 00008718<br />0313535A 0000AFA0<br />0313535C 00002419<br />0313535E 00000400<br />03135360 00003C04<br />03135362 0000803D<br />03135364 00003545<br />03135366 00006B28<br />03135368 00001319<br />0313536A 00000009<br />0313536C 00003506<br />0313536E 0000B170<br />03135370 00002419<br />03135372 00000800<br />03135374 00003504<br />03135376 0000B170<br />03135378 00003525<br />0313537A 00001C98<br />0313537C 00001719<br />0313537E 00000009<br />03135380 00003C06<br />03135382 0000803D<br />03135384 00008D4C<br />03135386 00005FE8<br />03135388 00008D2D<br />0313538A 00001158<br />0313538C 0000158D<br />0313538E 00000005<br />03135390 00008CC7<br />03135392 00000000<br />03135394 0000AC87<br />03135396 00000000<br />03135398 00002484<br />0313539A 00000004<br />0313539C 00001485<br />0313539E 0000FFFC<br />031353A0 000024C6<br />031353A2 00000004<br />031353A4 00008FBF<br />031353A6 0000000C<br />031353A8 000003E0<br />031353AA 00000008<br />031353AC 000027BD<br />031353AE 00000010</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Infinite Lives</span><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>011A539D 00000004</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Press D-pad Down To Die</span><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>291A5120 00000400<br />011A539E 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Skip Death Animation</span> [<a href="http://siglemic.net/resources" target="_blank" class="postlink">Vegard</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>030C2878 00000000<br />030C287A 00000000<br />030DCE68 00000000<br />030DCEA8 00000000<br />030DCEDC 00000000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Press D-pad Up To Have 0 Lives</span><br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>291A5120 00000800<br />011A539D 00000000<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Intro Skip</span> [Viper187]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>030B5D54 00002400</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Disable Music</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=320" class="postlink">Vegard</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>05187574 24050000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Always Display 50th Star Text Box After Grabbing A Star</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=323" class="postlink">Vegard</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>050C1578 00000000<br />050C159A 24060091</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Non Stop</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=21&amp;t=325" class="postlink">Vegard</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>030B5D54 00002400<br />050B7F9C 00000000<br />050B7F3C 00000000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Soft Reset</span> (L+R+Start) [abitalive]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>291A5120 00003010<br />031A53B8 00000004<br />011A53C8 00000001<br />011A53C9 00000001<br />E0000000 80008000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Spawn Switches Unpressed</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=20&amp;t=279&amp;p=2791#p2791" class="postlink">abitalive</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>0311112C 00001000</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Always Spawn Sub</span> [<a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=20&amp;t=279&amp;p=2791#p2795" class="postlink">abitalive</a>]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>0312BBD4 00001000<br />0317D860 00002400</code></dd></dl><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Always Spawn Mips</span> [abitalive]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>03162624 00002400</code></dd></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1488">abitalive</a> — 28 May 2014, 12:35</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
