<id>http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=281&amp;p=1852#p1852</id>
<link href="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=281&amp;p=1852#p1852"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Official Gecko Codes Thread]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://marioruns.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=281&amp;p=1852#p1852"><![CDATA[
VC-U<br /><br />Teleporter [Anarion]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>282085EA 00000002<br />92210000 011A532C<br />92210001 011A5330<br />92210002 011A5334<br />E0000000 80008000<br />282085EA 00008000<br />94210000 011A532C<br />94210001 011A5330<br />94210002 011A5334<br />E0000000 80008000<br /></code></dd></dl><br />Classic <img src="http://marioruns.com/forum/images/smilies/Controller.png" alt="Controller" title="Controller" />:<br />Press D-Pad LEFT to save current position.<br />Press D-Pad RIGHT to return to saved position.<br />Change 28208E5A to 291AXXXX for Gamecube controller.<br />Gamecube controller D-Pad values: <br />Down - 0400<br />Up - 0800<br />Left - 0200<br />Right - 0100<br /><br />Spawn Mario [Sharkbyte]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>291A5120 00000800<br />011A53C8 00000001<br />E0000000 80008000<br />291A5120 00000400<br />011A53C8 00000002<br />E0000000 80008000<br /></code></dd></dl><br />It's advised to press down and not up. Restarts the level quickly.<br /><br />Time how long it takes to get a star V1.1 (JS) GameShark converted by [mdmwii]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>050B3808 A03BB25E<br />050B7DFC A1A000EE<br />010B5317 00000040<br />050B3810 00000000<br />291A5120 00006010<br />031A53EC 00000000<br /></code></dd></dl><br />*Push L + R + B on gamecube controller to reset timer*<br />Change the 6010 to 0400 for down. Highly recommended if you use the spawn Mario code to restart the level quickly.<br /><br />Unlimited Health [GMO]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>011A539E 00000008<br /></code></dd></dl><br /><br /><br />Max Lives [GMO]<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>011A539D 00000064<br /></code></dd></dl><br />Some notes: I don't use the Max Lives code as it's already set back to 5 when I restart the level.<br />But feel free if you need it though.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://marioruns.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1450">speedruntrainer</a> — 02 May 2014, 15:33</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
